{{for|the market in Birmingham, England|Frankfurt Christmas Market, Birmingham}} [[File:Frankfurt Christmas market.jpg|thumb|upright|View of the market crowds at night in the main square of [[Römerberg (Frankfurt)|Römerberg]].]]
The '''Frankfurt Christmas Market''' (in [[German language|German]]: ''Frankfurter Weinachtmarkt''<ref name="leaflet14">{{citation| title=Frankfurter Weinachtmarkt – Frankfurt Christmas Market 23.11. – 22.12.2014 | publisher=Tourismus+Congress GmbH | location= Frankfurt am Main | date=2014 }}</ref>) is an annual outdoor [[Christmas market]] in central [[Frankfurt]], [[Hessen]], [[Germany]].<ref name="frankfurt-tourismus">{{cite web| url=http://www.frankfurt-tourismus.de/en/Discover-Experience/Events/Festivals-in-Frankfurt/Frankfurt-Christmas-Market | title=Frankfurt Christmas Market | website=[http://www.frankfurt-tourismus.de/ frankfurt-tourismus.de] | location=Germany | accessdate=18 December 2015 }}</ref>
The Christmas market opens in late November and continues until just before [[Christmas]] (normally 22 December) during [[Advent]]. It occupies a large area in central Frankfurt, including Friedrich-Stoltze-Platz, [[Hauptwache (Frankfurt am Main)|Hauptwache]] (to the north), Mainkai, [[Paulsplatz]], and [[Römerberg (Frankfurt)|Römerberg]] (to the south).<ref name="leaflet14" />
The market is one of the oldest such "Christkindchesmarkets" in Germany.<ref name="frankfurt-tourismus2">{{cite web| url=http://www.germany-insider-facts.com/frankfurt-christmas-market.html#.VJgRlV4gAA | title=Frankfurt Christmas Market | website=[http://www.germany-insider-facts.com/ germany-insider-facts.com] | accessdate=22 December 2014 }}</ref> Its origins date back to 1393.<ref name="frankfurt-tourismus3">{{cite web | url=http://www.frankfurt-tourismus.de/en/Discover-Experience/Festivals-in-Frankfurt/Frankfurt-Christmas-Markets-in-Great-Britain | title=Frankfurt Christmas Markets in Great Britain | website=[http://www.frankfurt-tourismus.de/ frankfurt-tourismus.de] | location=Germany | accessdate=22 December 2014 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141227214957/http://www.frankfurt-tourismus.de/en/Discover-Experience/Festivals-in-Frankfurt/Frankfurt-Christmas-Markets-in-Great-Britain | archivedate=27 December 2014 | df= }}</ref>
There are a number of affiliated markets, including in [[Frankfurt Christmas Market, Birmingham|Birmingham, England]].<ref name="frankfurt-tourismus2" />
